---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const page = {
  title: "Our Services | Edwards Landscape Group - Lawn Care & Landscaping in Lynchburg, VA",
  description: "Discover professional lawn care and landscaping services from Edwards Landscape Group. We offer mowing, mulching, aeration, fertilization, cleanups, and more for homes and businesses in Lynchburg and surrounding areas. Get a quote today!"
};
---

<BaseLayout {...page}>
<section class="page-hero" style="background-image: url('images/bg_3.jpg');">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-8 col-xl-6 hero-content-block">
              <div class="hero-kicker">Our services</div>
              <h1 class="mb-3">Everything your lawn and landscape need</h1>
              <p class="mb-4">From routine mowing to full landscape design, we tailor maintenance and enhancements to fit your property, schedule, and budget.</p>
              <div class="hero-actions d-flex flex-wrap">
                <a href="#services-list" class="btn btn-primary">Browse services</a>
                <a href="contact.html" class="btn btn-outline-light">Request a quote</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
   	
        <section class="ftco-section ftco-no-pt" id="services-list">
    	<div class="container" style="max-width: 2000px;">
    		<div class="row" style="justify-content: center; text-align: center;">
    			<div class="col-lg-9 services-wrap px-4 pt-5">
					<h2 class="mb-4" style="font-weight: 700;">Explore our services</h2>
    				<div class="d-flex align-items-stretch" id="Weekly Mowing">
						<div class="ftco-animate" style="width: 100%; height: 300px; overflow: hidden;">
							<img src="images/Mowing_Service.jpg" alt="mowing" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 15px;">
						</div>
						<div style="width: 10%;"></div>
						<div class="heading-section ftco-animate service-text" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; text-align: center;">
							<h2 class="mb-4">Weekly Mowing</h2>
                                                        <p>Weekly mowing is key to keeping your lawn looking neat and well-maintained all season long. Our professional mowing services ensure your grass stays at the perfect height for a healthy, manicured appearance.</p>
                                                        <p><a href="mowing.html" class="btn btn-primary py-3 px-4">Learn more</a></p>
						</div>
					</div>
    				<div class="service-item align-items-stretch" style="padding-top: 35px;" id="Fertilization and Weed Control">
						<div class="heading-section ftco-animate service-text" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; text-align: center;">
							<h2 class="mb-4">Fertilization and Weed Control</h2>
                                                        <p>Fertilization and weed control are essential for a lush, green lawn free from unwanted growth. Our services provide the right nutrients while eliminating weeds to keep your yard looking pristine.</p>
                                                        <p><a href="fertilization-weed-control.html" class="btn btn-primary py-3 px-4">Learn more</a></p>
						</div>
						<div style="width: 10%;"></div>
						<div class="ftco-animate" style="width: 100%; height: 300px; overflow: hidden;">
							<img src="images/Fertilization_Service.png" alt="mowing" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 15px;">
						</div>
					</div>
    				<div class="d-flex align-items-stretch" style="padding-top: 35px;" id="Aeration and Seeding">
						<div class="ftco-animate" style="width: 100%; height: 300px; overflow: hidden;">
							<img src="images/Aeration_Service.jpg" alt="mowing" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 15px;">
						</div>						
						<div style="width: 10%;"></div>
						<div class="heading-section ftco-animate service-text" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; text-align: center;">
							<h2 class="mb-4">Aeration and Seeding</h2>
                                                        <p>Aeration and seeding are key to revitalizing your lawn and promoting healthy growth. Our expert services help improve soil structure and ensure your grass gets the nutrients it needs to thrive.</p>
                                                        <p><a href="aeration-seeding.html" class="btn btn-primary py-3 px-4">Learn more</a></p>
						</div>
					</div>
    				<div class="service-item align-items-stretch" style="padding-top: 35px;" id="Fall and Winter Clean Up">
						<div class="heading-section ftco-animate service-text" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; text-align: center;">
							<h2 class="mb-4">Fall and Winter Clean Up</h2>
                                                        <p>Fall and winter clean-up is crucial for preparing your yard for the colder months. Our services remove leaves, debris, and dead plants, ensuring your landscape stays tidy and ready for spring</p>
                                                        <p><a href="fall-winter-cleanup.html" class="btn btn-primary py-3 px-4">Learn more</a></p>
						</div>
						<div style="width: 10%;"></div>
						<div class="ftco-animate" style="width: 100%; height: 300px; overflow: hidden;">
							<img src="images/FallCleanUp_Service.jpg" alt="mowing" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 15px;">
						</div>
					</div>
    				<div class="d-flex align-items-stretch" style="padding-top: 35px;" id="Mulching">
						<div class="ftco-animate" style="width: 100%; height: 300px; overflow: hidden;">
							<img src="images/Mulching_Service.jpg" alt="mowing" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 15px;">
						</div>						
						<div style="width: 10%;"></div>
						<div class="heading-section ftco-animate service-text" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; text-align: center;">
							<h2 class="mb-4">Mulching</h2>
                                                        <p>Mulching is essential for maintaining healthy soil and vibrant plants in your garden. Our mulching services help retain moisture, reduce weeds, and provide your landscape with a polished, finished look.</p>
                                                        <p><a href="mulching.html" class="btn btn-primary py-3 px-4">Learn more</a></p>
						</div>
					</div>
                                        <div class="service-item align-items-stretch" style="padding-top: 35px;" id="Hardscaping">
						<div class="heading-section ftco-animate service-text" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; text-align: center;">
							<h2 class="mb-4">Bed Maintenance</h2>
                                                        <p>A well-maintained flower bed can be the highlight of your garden, but it needs constant care to flourish. We provide expert flower bed maintenance to keep your flowers blooming beautifully all season long.</p>
                                                        <p><a href="bed-maintenance.html" class="btn btn-primary py-3 px-4">Learn more</a></p>
						</div>
						  
						<div style="width: 10%;"></div>
						<div class="ftco-animate" style="width: 100%; height: 300px; overflow: hidden;">
							<img src="images/Bed_Service.jpg" alt="mowing" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 15px;">
						</div>
					</div>
                                        <div class="d-flex align-items-stretch" style="padding-top: 35px;" id="Landscaping">
						<div class="ftco-animate" style="width: 100%; height: 300px; overflow: hidden;">
							<img src="images/ShrubCare_Service.jpg" alt="mowing" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 15px;">
						</div>						
						<div style="width: 10%;"></div>
						<div class="heading-section ftco-animate service-text" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; text-align: center;">
							<h2 class="mb-4">Tree and Shrub Care</h2>
                                                        <p>Keeping your trees and shrubs healthy is essential to maintaining a vibrant landscape. Our expert care services help protect them from disease and pests, ensuring they thrive throughout the seasons.</p>
                                                        <p><a href="tree-shrub-care.html" class="btn btn-primary py-3 px-4">Learn more</a></p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="service-item align-items-stretch" style="padding-top: 35px;" id="Bed Maintenance">
						<div class="heading-section ftco-animate service-text" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; text-align: center;">
							<h2 class="mb-4">Hardscaping</h2>
                                                        <p>A beautifully designed yard starts with solid structure. Our expert hardscaping services bring lasting style and function to your outdoor space—from elegant stone pathways to durable retaining walls—so your landscape stays stunning year-round with less upkeep.</p>
                                                        <p><a href="hardscaping.html" class="btn btn-primary py-3 px-4">Learn more</a></p>
						</div>
						  
						<div style="width: 10%;"></div>
						<div class="ftco-animate" style="width: 100%; height: 300px; overflow: hidden;">
							<img src="images/Landscaping_Service.jpg" alt="mowing" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 15px;">
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="d-flex align-items-stretch" style="padding-top: 35px;" id="Tree and Shrub Care">
						<div class="ftco-animate" style="width: 100%; height: 300px; overflow: hidden;">
							<img src="images/Landscape_Design_Service.jpg" alt="mowing" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 15px;">
						</div>						
						<div style="width: 10%;"></div>
						<div class="heading-section ftco-animate service-text" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; text-align: center;">
							<h2 class="mb-4">Landscape Design</h2>
                                                        <p>A great yard doesn’t happen by accident—it’s designed. Our professional landscape design services transform your outdoor space with thoughtful layouts, plant selections, and features that reflect your style and enhance your home’s curb appeal, season after season.</p>
                                                        <p><a href="landscaping.html" class="btn btn-primary py-3 px-4">Learn more</a></p>
